lead_paragraph: Wallabies coach Michael Cheika has shrugged off Australia's struggles in Super Rugby this season and hit back at critics for being too pessimistic about the local game in the lead-up to the home test series against England.

headline.print_headline: Wallabies Coach Cheika Dismisses Australia Doom-Mongers
